6. PROHIBITION OF AI/ML TRAINING

  a) Training Prohibition:
     The use of this Software, its source code, documentation, or any
     associated materials as training data for artificial intelligence,
     machine learning models, large language models (LLMs), neural networks,
     or any other form of automated learning system is strictly prohibited
     without explicit written permission from the Author.

  b) Scope:
     This prohibition applies to, but is not limited to:
     - Direct ingestion of source code into training datasets
     - Web scraping or crawling of this repository for ML purposes
     - Embedding generation or vectorization for AI retrieval systems
     - Fine-tuning or transfer learning using this codebase
     - Any derivative dataset creation that includes this Software

  c) Consequences of Violation:
     Any violation of this Section constitutes a material breach and shall
     result in:

     (i)   Immediate and automatic termination of all rights granted under
           this License;

     (ii)  An obligation to pay a commercial licensing fee of EUR 2,500,000
           (two million five hundred thousand Euros) per AI/ML model trained
           using this Software;

     (iii) An obligation to immediately cease distribution, deployment, and
           use of any AI/ML model trained in violation of this Section;

     (iv)  Liability for all damages, including but not limited to lost
           licensing revenue, legal costs, and consequential damages.

  d) Detection and Audit:
     The Author reserves the right to request reasonable evidence from any
     party that this Software has not been used for AI/ML training purposes.

